    "title": "Lead Revenue Manager at Goa Tourism Holdings Services",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Revenue Manager with drive and ambition, Goa Tourism Holdings Services in Hyderabad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Goa Tourism Holdings Services:\nGoa Tourism Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Goa Tourism Holdings Services!",
